@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh; /* Позволява съдържанието да расте над видимата част */
        overflow-x: hidden; /* Скрива само хоризонталното преливане */
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)), url('/images/background.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-attachment: fixed; /* Прави фона фиксиран */
        color: black; /* Примерен цвят на текста */
    }

    .image-container {
        display: flex; /* Подрежда снимките хоризонтално */
        justify-content: space-around; /* Разстояние между снимките */
        margin: 20px;
    }

    .image-box {
        text-align: center; /* Центрира надписите под снимките */
    }

        .image-box img {
            width: 200px; /* Примерен размер за снимките */
            height: auto;
            border: none; /* Добавя рамка към снимките */
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

    .caption {
        margin-top: 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>

<center><h1>About Us</h1></center>

<center>
    <p>
    <br />
    Behind every great human achievement, there is a team.
    <br /> <br />
    From medicine and space travel, to online bakery and pizza deliveries, our products help teams all over the planet advance humanity through the power of software.
    <br /> <br />
    Our mission is to provide a comprehensive and intuitive tool that helps teams stay organized, meet deadlines, and achieve their goals.
    </p>
</center>

<p>
    <center><h3>Our believes and values...</h3></center>
    <div class="image-container">
        <div class="image-box">
            <img src="images/idealistic.png" alt="Image 1">
            <div class="caption">Simplicity and Ease of Use</div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-box">
            <img src="images/flexibility.png" alt="Image 2">
            <div class="caption">Flexibility and Adaptability</div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-box">
            <img src="images/group.png" alt="Image 3">
            <div class="caption">Transparency and Collaboration</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</p>

